data.description: Uncover your perfect retreat! This 3BR, 2BA beauty, built in 2005, graces nearly an acre of serene potential. This property offers both move-in readiness and limitless possibilities for transformation. Relax on your covered front porch or cookout on the rear rebuilt deck overlooking the large fenced-in backyard. Features a wired storage building (electricity not functioning), custom closet cabinetry in the primary bedroom, and new luxury vinyl laminate floors in the living room and kitchen area. This is in great location just minutes away from shopping and downtown Lincolnton!
